h3-ios-native-sdks-now-come-through-swif.translation:
```json showLineNumbers title="app.json"
{
  "expo": {
    "plugins": [
      [
        "expo-build-properties",
        {
          "ios": {
            "useFrameworks": "dynamic"
          }
        }
      ]
    ]
  }
}
```

Ardından eklentiyi yükleyin ve native projeyi yeniden oluşturun:

```bash showLineNumbers
npx expo install expo-build-properties
npx expo prebuild --clean
```

#### Bare React Native \{#bare-react-native\}

iOS hedefinize dinamik framework'leri ekleyin, ardından pod'ları yeniden yükleyin:

```ruby showLineNumbers title="ios/Podfile"
use_frameworks! :linkage => :dynamic
```

h3-getpaywall-getflow-pe3b0c442.translation:
```diff showLineNumbers
- const paywall = await adapty.getPaywallForDefaultAudience('YOUR_PLACEMENT_ID', 'en');
